Package: NEONiso
Type: Package
Title: Download, calibrate, and analyze NEON Atmospheric Isotope Flux Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rich Fiorella
Maintainer: Rich Fiorella <rich.fiorella@utah.edu>
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Description: This package provides functions for downloading,
    calibrating, and analyzing NEON data, with a particular focus
    on the atmospheric isotope and eddy covariance data.
License: Until further notice, please do not distribute outside of the SPATIAL Group
    and immediate collaborators on the NEON Transpiration Grant.
